					<description><![CDATA[Hello lovelies.  Today, I thought it was time for something delightfully strange.  I ran across these awesome surreal gifs on Tumblr, thanks to paqosdragons, and thought I&#8217;d share them here.  Artist Kevin Weir makes these wonderful gifs from old photographs he gets from the library of congress.  Now this is exactly why I love royalty free archives. [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2670" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo3_500.gif" alt="" width="500" height="431" /></p>
<p>Hello lovelies.  Today, I thought it was time for something delightfully strange.  I ran across these awesome surreal gifs on Tumblr, thanks to <a href="http://paqosdragons.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">paqosdragons</a>, and thought I&#8217;d share them here.  Artist <a href="http://www.kevinjweir.com/" target="_blank">Kevin Weir</a> makes these wonderful gifs from old photographs he gets from the library of congress.  Now this is exactly why I love royalty free archives.  It opens up a world of endless possibilities for really clever and strange delights.</p>
<p><a href="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_n17etjr3YK1qk4ealo1_500.gif"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2678" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_n17etjr3YK1qk4ealo1_500.gif" alt="" width="450" height="357" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo10_r1_400.gif"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2677" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo10_r1_400.gif" alt="" width="400" height="568" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo4_500.gif"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2671" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo4_500.gif" alt="" width="450" height="587" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo5_r1_500.gif"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2672" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo5_r1_500.gif" alt="" width="500" height="500" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo1_400.gif"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2668" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo1_400.gif" alt="" width="397" height="526" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo7_r1_400.gif"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2674" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/tumblr_nbpb85vvRv1qlq9poo7_r1_400.gif" alt="" width="325" height="428" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Do you like my top picks?  Check out more of Kevin Weir&#8217;s artwork on <a href="http://www.kevinjweir.com/" target="_blank">his main site</a> and his <a href="http://fluxmachine.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">Tumblr blog</a>.  Don&#8217;t forget to share your favorites!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
