ved-social-image synved-social-image-share" title="Share Twist on Tumblr" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/plugins/social-media-feather/synved-social/image/social/regular/24x24/tumblr.png" alt="tumblr" width="24" height="24" /></a>  Thanks again lovelies for always being awesome and sharing as much as you do.  It really helps.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
